     - However,[0m[2m `[0m[2mde[0m[2mcrement()` can[0m[2m still[0m[2m be called by[0m[2m more coroutines than[0m[2m stock allows[0m[2m because `[0m[2mcheck_stock()` let[0m[2m them all through[0m[2m
     - Actually[0m[2m, `decrement[0m[2m()` re[0m[2mchecks[0m[2m stock, so it[0m[2m shouldn't go negative[0m[2m... unless the[0m[2m TO[0m[2mCTOU between `[0m[2mcheck_stock()` and[0m[2m `decrement()`[0m[2m causes[0m[2m more charges[0m[2m than items[0m[2m
     
