     This way[0m[2m, multiple[0m[2m coroutines can do[0m[2m their[0m[2m "[0m[2mI[0m[2m/O" (sleep[0m[2m) concurrently, but[0m[2m the actual[0m[2m check-and-mod[0m[2mify is serialized[0m[2m by[0m[2m the lock.
     
     **[0m[2mBug 2:[0m[2m Ghost charges**[0m[2m
     - `checkout[0m[2m()` calls `check[0m[2m_stock()` first[0m[2m, then `charge[0m[2m()`, then `[0m[2mdecrement()`[0m[2m
