     - Result[0m[2m: customer was charged[0m[2m but received[0m[2m no item
     
     **[0m[2mFix for[0m[2m both[0m[2m bugs:**[0m[2m
     
     The pattern[0m[2m should[0m[2m be: **reserve[0m[2m inventory[0m[2m first, then charge[0m[2m, then release reservation[0m[2m on failure**[0m[2m.
     
     1. `[0m[2mreserve(quantity)` —[0m[2m atomically check[0m[2m-and[0m[2m-decrement stock[0m[2m (under[0m[2m lock)
     2.[0m[2m `[0m[2mcharge()` — attempt[0m[2m payment
