  **[0m[2mRoot cause[0m[2m analysis:**
     
     1[0m[2m. **Ghost[0m[2m charges**:[0m[2m `checkout()` does[0m[2m check[0m[2m_stock[0m[2m → charge → decrement[0m[2m as[0m[2m three separate `[0m[2mawait`-[0m[2myield[0m[2ming steps. Under[0m[2m concurrency, all[0m[2m 12 orders pass `[0m[2mcheck_stock()` ([0m[2mstock=5),[0m[2m ~[0m[2m10[0m[2m succeed at `charge[0m[2m()`, then[0m[2m only 5 can[0m[2m `decrement()`[0m[2m — leaving[0m[2m 5 customers[0m[2m charged with[0m[2m no item.
     
